  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV27">
<l>cēmañceṅ kōṉaru ḷēceru vārunaṭ pākuvareṉ</l>
<l>ṟēmam peṟavaiyañ collumey yēpaṇṭel lāmaṟaikū</l>
<l>yāmaṅka ṭōṟeri vīcunaṅ kaṇṇaṉ taṇṇantuḻāyt</l>
<l>tāmam puṉaiyavav vāṭaiyī tōvantu taṇṇeṉṟatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>“Protection is the grace of a just king. Even among enemies there will be friendship”,</l>
<l>thus pleasurably the world speaks true. That north wind that at all former times flung flames every midnight,</l> 
<l>calling out the beats  – when one is decorated</l>
<l>with a string of our Kaṇṇaṉ’s pretty cool Tulsi, this?, it comes [and] is cool.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
